 death]]\n[[Category:Western Christianity]]\n", "name_user": "Jzsj", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eHistory of the belief:ce", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Purgatory"}
{"title_page": "Luis Pedro da Silva Ferreira", "text_new": "{{short description|Angolan footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name          = Luis Pedro\n| image          =\n| fullname       = Luis Pedro da Silva Ferreira\n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1992|01|6|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Malanje]], [[Angola]]\n| height         = {{height|m=1.84}}\n| position       = [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|Centre back]]\n| currentclub    = \n| clubnumber     = \n| youthyears1    =\n| youthclubs1 = \n| years1         = 2011\u20132013\n| clubs1         = [[FC Groningen]]\n| caps1          = 4\n| goals1         = 0\n| years2         = 2012\u20132013\n| clubs2         = \u2192 [[SC Veendam]] (loan)\n| caps2          = 24\n| goals2         = 0\n| years3         = 2013\u20132015\n| clubs3         = [[FC Emmen]]\n| caps3          = 72\n| goals3         = 3\n| years4         = 2015\u20132016\n| clubs4         = [[NAC Breda]]\n| caps4          = 32\n| goals4         = 4\n| years5         = 2016\u20132017\n| clubs5         = [[De Graafschap]]\n| caps5          = 3\n| goals5         = 0\n| pcupdate       = 21 May 2017\n}}\n\n'''Luis Pedro da Silva Ferreira''' (born 6 January 1992 in [[Malanje]], Angola) is an Angolan [[football (soccer)|football]] player who last played as a [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|centre back]] for [[De Graafschap]]. He formerly played for [[FC Groningen]], [[SC Veendam]], [[FC Emmen]] and [[De Graafschap]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://eredivisielive.nl/eredivisie/speler/949218/luis-pedro/|title=Een abonnement op FOX Sports naar keuze. Abonneer nu|website=eredivisielive.nl|language=nl|access-date=2017-07-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/luis-pedro_3/|title=Luis Pedro|website=worldfootball.net|language=en-GB|access-date=2017-07-11}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2012}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.vi.nl/spelers/carriere/luis-pedro-da-