le=Een abonnement op FOX Sports naar keuze. Abonneer nu|website=eredivisielive.nl|language=nl|access-date=2017-07-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/luis-pedro_3/|title=Luis Pedro|website=worldfootball.net|language=en-GB|access-date=2017-07-11}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2012}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.vi.nl/spelers/carriere/luis-pedro-da-silva-ferreira.htm Voetbal International profile] {{in lang|nl}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ferreira, Luis Pedro da Silva}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Malanje]]\n[[Category:Angolan footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:FC Groningen players]]\n[[Category:SC Veendam players]]\n[[Category:FC Emmen players]]\n[[Category:NAC Breda players]]\n[[Category:De Graafschap players]]\n[[Category:Eredivisie players]]\n[[Category:Eerste Divisie players]]\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Angolan footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Angolan football player\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luis_Pedro_da_Silva_Ferreira"}
